(9791, 'en', 'default', '72767e68111ba9fb4df1168920eff12d', 'The new block-based editor won&#8217;t change the way any of your content looks to your visitors. What it will do is let you insert any type of multimedia in a snap and rearrange to your heart&#8217;s content. Each piece of content will be in its own block; a distinct wrapper for easy maneuvering. If you&#8217;re more of an HTML and CSS sort of person, then the blocks won&#8217;t stand in your way. WordPress is here to simplify the process, not the outcome.', NULL, NULL, 'LINE', NULL, 10, '', '877acacd060197a0b2c3e994bebc9495', NULL, ''),
